script.name: plugin.shiprename.cmd.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.cycrow.shiprename' $shiprename.data = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='shiprename' if not $shiprename.data $shiprename.data = table alloc $current.name = 'Your [maker] [type][variant| ]' $shiprename.data['name'] = $current.name $a.obj ->set local variable: name='shiprename' value=$shiprename.data end $shiprename.global = get global variable: name='shiprename' if not $shiprename.global $shiprename.global = table alloc set global variable: name='shiprename' value=$shiprename.global end
$company.name = $shiprename.global['company'] $company.id = $shiprename.global['company.id'] $group.closed = $shiprename.global['closed'] if not $group.closed $group.closed = table alloc $shiprename.global['closed'] = $group.closed end
$current.name = $shiprename.data['name'] $short.name = $shiprename.data['short'] $station.id = $shiprename.data['id'] skip if $station.id $station.id = 0 $ship.ids = $shiprename.data['shipid'] if not $ship.ids $ship.ids = table alloc $shiprename.data['shipid'] = $ship.ids end
$variables = table alloc $variables['add.type'] = '[type]' $variables['add.maker'] = '[maker]' $variables['add.variant'] = '[variant]' $variables['add.company'] = '[company]' $variables['add.companyid'] = '[initials]' $variables['add.short'] = '[short]' $variables['add.homebase'] = '[homebase]' $variables['add.shipid'] = '[shipid]' $variables['add.stationid'] = '[stationid]' $variables['add.cmd'] = '[cmd]' $variables['add.cmdshort'] = '[cmd.short]' $variables['add.tradeskill'] = '[tradeskill]' $variables['add.flags'] = '[flags]' $variables['add.sector'] = '[sector]' $variables['add.class'] = '[class]' $variables['add.cargo'] = '[cargo]'
$colours = table alloc $colours['add.red'] = '[red]' $colours['add.blue'] = '[blue]' $colours['add.green'] = '[green]' $colours['add.yellow'] = '[yellow]' $colours['add.cyan'] = '[cyan]' $colours['add.magenta'] = '[magenta]' $colours['add.grey'] = '[grey]' $colours['add.white'] = '[white]'
$variaibles.name = table alloc $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=200 $variaibles.name['[type]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=201 $variaibles.name['[variant]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=202 $variaibles.name['[maker]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=203 $variaibles.name['[company]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=204 $variaibles.name['[initials]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=205 $variaibles.name['[short]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=206 $variaibles.name['[homebase]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=207 $variaibles.name['[cmd]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=208 $variaibles.name['[cmd.short]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=209 $variaibles.name['[shipid]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=210 $variaibles.name['[stationid]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=211 $variaibles.name['[tradeskill]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=212 $variaibles.name['[sector]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=213 $variaibles.name['[flags]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=214 $variaibles.name['[class]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=215 $variaibles.name['[cargo]'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=216 $variaibles.name['[fulltype]'] = $read.text
$colour.values = table alloc $colour.values['[red]'] = 10 $colour.values['[blue]'] = 11 $colour.values['[green]'] = 12 $colour.values['[yellow]'] = 13 $colour.values['[cyan]'] = 14 $colour.values['[magenta]'] = 15 $colour.values['[grey]'] = 16 $colour.values['[white]'] = 17
$presets = array alloc: size=2 $presets[0] = 'Your [maker] [type][variant| ]' $presets[1] = '[company] [type] #[stationid]-[shipid]'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Switch] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'shiprename.menu' if is datatype[ $selection ] == DATATYPE_SHIP $ship.ids[$selection] = $value else if $selection == 'station.id' $station.id = $value end gosub sub.SaveVariables gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Group] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] $current.group = null if $menu.id == 'shiprename.menu' $current.group = $group.closed else if $menu.id == 'shiprename.variable' $current.group = $group.closed end if $current.group if $value remove key $selection from table $current.group else $current.group[$selection] = [TRUE] end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $value if $menu.id == 'shiprename.menu' if $selection == 'edit.str' $current.name = $value else if $selection == 'company.name' $company.name = $value else if $selection == 'company.id' $company.id = $value else if $selection == 'short' $short.name = $value else if $selection == 'shiprename.preset' $current.name = $value else if $selection == 'shiprename.variable' $append = $variables[$value] skip if $append $append = $colours[$value] if $append $current.name = $current.name + $append end end
gosub sub.SaveVariables gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end
else if $a.event == 'add.variable' gosub sub.BuildVariableMenu return $input
else if $a.event == 'set.preset' gosub sub.BuildPresentMenu return $input
else if $a.event == 'edit' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=300 $input = create input: id='edit.str', user input=Var/String, refobj=null, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$a.data return $input
else if $a.event == 'company.name' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=301 $input = create input: id=$a.event, user input=Var/String, refobj=null, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$a.data return $input else if $a.event == 'company.id' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=302 $input = create input: id=$a.event, user input=Var/String, refobj=null, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$a.data return $input else if $a.event == 'short' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=303 $input = create input: id=$a.event, user input=Var/String, refobj=null, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$a.data return $input else if $a.event == 'shiprename.menu' do if is datatype[ $a.data ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $a.data = $a.data[0] if $a.data == 'start' return [TRUE] end else if $a.event == [MEvent.Arguments] $ret = create new array, arguments=$current.name, null, null, null, null return $ret
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished]
end
return null
sub.BuildMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
$COL1 = 120
$text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=20 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$current.name $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.columns
@ $example.name = [THIS] -> call script plugin.shiprename.renameobj : Object=[PLAYERSHIP] Name String=$current.name Station ID=$station.id Ship ID=1 Company Name=$company.name Company Initials=$company.id Station Shortname=$short.name $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=21 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$example.name $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.columns
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=50 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text
if $group.closed['global'] $is.open = [FALSE] else $is.open = [TRUE] end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=51 add new grouping to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, open=$is.open, id='global', indent=10 $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=22 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text if $company.name $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$company.name else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=9 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text end $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.columns nextinput='company.name' value=$company.name
$text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=23 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text if $company.name $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$company.id else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=9 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text end $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.columns nextinput='company.id' value=$company.id add end grouping to menu: $menu
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=52 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s', $read.text, $a.obj, null, null, null if $group.closed['station'] $is.open = [FALSE] else $is.open = [TRUE] end add new grouping to menu: $menu, text=$text, open=$is.open, id='station', indent=20
$text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=24 $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text if $short.name $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$short.name else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=9 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text end $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.columns nextinput='short' value=$short.name
$values.array = array alloc: size=100 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=9 $values.array[0] = $read.text $i = 1 while $i < 100 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s', $i, null, null, null, null $values.array[$i] = $text inc $i = end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=25 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$values.array, default=$station.id, return id='station.id', width=80 allowtabs=[FALSE] add end grouping to menu: $menu
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=53 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=26 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text nextinput='edit' value=$current.name $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=27 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text nextinput='add.variable' value=null $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=28 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text nextinput='set.preset' value=null add section to custom menu: $menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=29 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue='start'
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=54 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text $ships = $a.obj -> get owned ships: class/type=Ship if not $ships $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else if not size of array $ships $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $sorted.array = sort array $ships $sorted.i = 0 $sorted.size = size of array $sorted.array while $sorted.i < $sorted.size $item = $sorted.array[$sorted.i] inc $sorted.i = $values.array = clone array: $values.array $ship.ids = $shiprename.data['shipid'] $current.id = $ship.ids[$item] skip if $current.id $current.id = 0 $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text = $item ->create custom menu string object icon $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[0] = $text $text = $item -> get name $text = create custom menu column string, position=10 length=400 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.columns[1] = $text add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$text.columns, value array=$values.array, default=$current.id, return id=$item, width=80 allowtabs=[FALSE] end end
set menu option: $menu, remove main header=[TRUE] set menu option: $menu, icon=49 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Big]
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1 $callback = [Callback.Switch] | [Callback.Group] $input = create input: id='shiprename.menu' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=$callback endsub
sub.SaveVariables: $shiprename.data['id'] = $station.id $shiprename.data['short'] = $short.name $shiprename.data['name'] = $current.name $shiprename.global['company'] = $company.name $shiprename.global['company.id'] = $company.id endsub
sub.UpdateMenu: gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input endsub
sub.BuildPresentMenu: $menu = create custom menu array $COL1 = 120
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=55 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=56 $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text
$size = size of array $presets $i = 0 while $i < $size $v = $presets[$i] inc $i = $text = sprintf: fmt='%s. %s', $i, $v, null, null, null @ $example.name = [THIS] -> call script plugin.shiprename.renameobj : Object=[PLAYERSHIP] Name String=$v Station ID=$station.id Ship ID=1 Company Name=$company.name Company Initials=$company.id Station Shortname=$short.name $text = create text for custom menu, left=$text, right=$example.name add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$v end
set menu option: $menu, icon=49 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge]
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3 $input = create input: id='shiprename.preset' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
sub.BuildVariableMenu: $menu = create custom menu array
$COL1 = 120
if $group.closed['variables'] $is.open = [FALSE] else $is.open = [TRUE] end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=57 add new grouping to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, open=$is.open, id='variables', indent=10 $table = $variables gosub sub.DrawVariables add end grouping to menu: $menu if $group.closed['colours'] $is.open = [FALSE] else $is.open = [TRUE] end add section to custom menu: $menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=58 add new grouping to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, open=$is.open, id='colours', indent=10 $table = $colours gosub sub.DrawVariables add end grouping to menu: $menu
set menu option: $menu, icon=49 set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Big]
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=2 $input = create input: id='shiprename.variable' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$a.obj callback=null endsub
sub.DrawVariables: $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$table $sorted.i = 0 $sorted.size = size of array $sorted.array while $sorted.i < $sorted.size $item = $sorted.array[$sorted.i] inc $sorted.i =
$v = $table[$item]
$text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text.id = $colour.values[$v] if $text.id $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=$text.id, $v, null, null, null, null else $read.text = $v end $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=$COL1 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[0] = $text $read.text = $variaibles.name[$v] skip if $read.text $read.text = ' ' $text = create custom menu column string, position=$COL1 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.columns[1] = $text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.columns returnvalue=$item end endsub
return null
